{"tid":1415904,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"我哋唔係要贏連登，我哋係要贏香港啊","createTime":"2019-08-05T14:21:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-05T14:23:59.000Z","uid":179547,"like":14,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"b20dc39bbe1b1b07b022fbd26a32ab3421b55c5c","tid":1415904,"uid":179547,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T14:21:20.000Z","msg":"呢度大家係真連登仔，你掟核彈都唔撚割蓆，但社會上其他人點諗？<br />\n<br />\n香港好大，唔好淨係上連登打飛機啦，我哋要贏香港啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">對準政權，對準黑警<br />\n<br />\n永不割蓆，但有時要停一停，諗一諗</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n《梁天琦致香港人》<br />\n<br />\n你們或許因而心中充滿憤怒，這乃是人之常情。但我懇請你們不要被仇恨支配自己，在危難中，仍要時刻保持警覺與思考。<br />\n<br />\n政治的工作不只是要令支持自己的人繼續支持自己，而更是要令不支持自己的人轉為支持自己，改變想法，認同自己的方向。"},{"pid":"fca4b223c23b39ae2e3920a8b7da3037ffacbdf6","tid":1415904,"uid":179547,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T14:21:44.000Z","msg":"寧阻人返工，勿阻人收工<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1414145\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1414145</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"3187e8c5542faff20eb1ac17fdd648df784caa76","tid":1415904,"uid":299311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T14:22:08.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"1a97a846c16e8698219823e7e9ffb8527b3cbd2d","tid":1415904,"uid":140738,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T14:23:59.000Z","msg":"唔好墮入同溫層陷阱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}